    m_Alignment: 0
    m_AlignByGeometry: 0
    m_RichText: 1
    m_HorizontalOverflow: 0
    m_VerticalOverflow: 0
    m_LineSpacing: 1
  m_Text: "HOW TO PLAY: \n\nIn DodgeHero, the point of the game is to dodge the attacks
    of the enemy in front of you. At the start of the game the enemy will lift up
    their blade in the opposite side of their attack and one of the 4 arrows will
    light up in blue. Your goal is to dodge the attack by pressing W,A,S, or D to
    the corrosponding blue signal arrow that you are shown. This proccess will continue
    to repeate as the game will also speed up. The game will continue until the player
    has missed a dodge 3 times."
